1. Download the CBMC source code as follows:

   svn co http://www.cprover.org/svn/cbmc/releases/cbmc-4.0

2. Make sure that compiles, according to the instructions that come
   with it.

3. Now open the file config.inc in the Satabs source directory
   and adjust the variable CBMC to point to the location of the CBMC
   directory created by step 1.

4. Now do

   make

5. Recall that you need to obtain a model checker for the Boolean program.
   We recommend you try boom, available at http://www.cprover.org/boom/
